snippet.textDisplay: "'Piya Calling' is a groundbreaking masterpiece! The blend of Turkish, Arabic, Norwegian,Urdu, Gujarati, and Balochi languages is a testament to the power of music to unite cultures and transcend borders. The way the singers seamlessly switch between languages is awe-inspiring. The song's message of love and longing is universal and resonates deeply. Coke Studio Pakistan has outdone itself with this multilingual marvel. Kudos to the talented artists and team for creating something so extraordinary!" Keep up the good work Coke Studio you make us all proud 👍🎉
